Third-party software
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This tool keeps a minimal dependency surface. Required: "ajv" (MIT) and
"@clack/prompts" (MIT). Optional, lazily loaded only when the corresponding
provider or file type is used: "openai" (Apache-2.0), "@huggingface/transformers"
(Apache-2.0), "mammoth" (BSD-2-Clause), "pdfjs-dist" (Apache-2.0). Each remains
the property of its respective authors and is used under its own license.

